# Prytula design system

## Figma source

- **File:** [Prytula-Responsive](https://www.figma.com/design/hiAQiy4aRZQiwD1S4jekxY/Prytula-Responsive) — `fileKey`: `hiAQiy4aRZQiwD1S4jekxY`
- **Modes:** Mode 1 only (no light/dark / breakpoint modes in variables)

## Three collections

| Collection | Figma paths | CSS output | Use in components |
|------------|-------------|------------|-------------------|
| **Brand** | `neutral/500`, `orange/500`, `Scale/300`, `font-size/400`, … | `--pryt-brand-{slug}` | **Never directly** — internal primitives |
| **Alias** | `bg/page`, `space/medium`, `action/donate`, … | `--{slug}` | **Yes** — public API when no Mapped slot exists |
| **Mapped** | `Surface/surface-page`, `Text/text-default`, … | `--{category}-{slot}` | **Yes — preferred** for UI roles |

**Chain:** `Mapped → Alias → Brand` (literal). Brand has no incoming aliases.

**Alias literals (not Brand refs):** `radius/round` (9999px), `size/4xlarge` (44px).

---

## Token-to-CSS mapping

| Figma | CSS function | Example |
|-------|--------------|---------|
| Brand `orange/500` | `brandVar()` | `--pryt-brand-orange-500` |
| Alias `space/medium` | `aliasVar()` | `--space-medium` |
| Alias `bg/page` | `aliasVar()` | `--bg-page` |
| Mapped `Text/text-default` | `mappedVar()` | `--text-default` (strips duplicate `text-` prefix) |
| Mapped `Surface/surface-page` | `mappedVar()` | `--surface-page` |
| Mapped `Border/on-inverse` | `mappedVar()` | `--border-on-inverse` |
| App-only stack | manual in `index.css` | `--font-display` |

**Convention:** slashes in Figma → hyphens in CSS. Mapped category is lowercased (`Surface` → `surface-`).

---

## Token pipeline (generated CSS)

1. **Source:** `design-tokens/data/figma-variables.tsv` (export from Figma)
2. **Build:** `npm run build:tokens` → runs `design-tokens/scripts/build.mjs`
3. **Outputs (identical content):**
   - `design-tokens/dist/tokens.css` + `tokens.ts`
   - `web/src/styles/tokens.css` (imported in `web/src/main.tsx`)
4. **Git:** both CSS paths are **gitignored** — regenerate after clone or TSV update

Do **not** hand-edit generated `tokens.css`. Change TSV or `build.mjs`, then rebuild.

---

## Token aliasing / dedupe

Five Mapped tokens share the **same CSS variable name** as their Alias target. `build.mjs` emits **one** `:root` line (from Alias); Mapped rows are omitted from CSS but remain in `tokens.ts`.

| CSS variable | Alias Figma path | Mapped Figma path | Value chain |
|--------------|------------------|-------------------|-------------|
| `--border-default` | `border/default` | `Border/default` | → neutral/200 |
| `--border-strong` | `border/strong` | `Border/strong` | → neutral/950 |
| `--border-focus` | `border/focus` | `Border/focus` | → blue/700 |
| `--text-disabled` | `text/disabled` | `Text/text-disabled` | → neutral/300 |
| `--text-link` | `text/link` | `Text/text-link` | → blue/950 |

**Not a bug:** Figma has two paths, CSS has one variable. Use `--border-default` (etc.) freely in components. Do not invent a second name or duplicate `:root` entry.

**Non-colliding example:** `Border/on-inverse` → `--border-on-inverse` (Alias is `border/inverse` → `--border-inverse`).

---

## Component token rules (forbidden patterns)

1. **Never** hardcode colors, spacing, radii, or font-sizes (no raw `#hex`, `rgb()`, `12px` for tokens that exist in the system).
2. **Never** use `--pryt-brand-*` directly in product or design-system components — only through Alias or Mapped.
3. **Preference order:**
   - **First:** Mapped (`--text-default`, `--surface-page`, `--surface-action`, …)
   - **Then:** Alias (`--space-medium`, `--radius-round`, `--action-donate`, …) when no Mapped exists
   - **Last resort:** Brand only with an inline comment explaining why
4. **App font:** `var(--font-display)` — defined in `web/src/index.css`, not from Figma export

