## Brand primitives (103)

Low-level palette and scale — **do not reference in components.**

- **Palettes:** `neutral/*`, `blue/*`, `orange/*`, `green/*`, `red/*`, `chart/brown-*`, `chart/blue-*`
- **Scale:** `Scale/0` … `Scale/3200` (spacing primitives, px)
- **Typography:** `font-family/*`, `font-weight/*`, `font-size/*`

CSS pattern: `--pryt-brand-{category}-{step}` e.g. `--pryt-brand-orange-500`, `--pryt-brand-scale-300`, `--pryt-brand-font-size-400`.

Product pages may use `--pryt-brand-font-size-*` for typography until Mapped text styles exist — prefer Mapped/Alias for colors and layout.

