## Semantic notes (Figma → meaning)

| Token | Typical use |
|-------|-------------|
| `--surface-page` | Page background (warm off-white) |
| `--surface-action` / `--action-donate` | Orange donate CTA |
| `--accent-primary` | Brand blue (dark) |
| `--accent-secondary` | Brand orange |
| `--text-default` | Body text on light surfaces |

There is **no** `--brand-primary` in this file — do not invent legacy names from old docs.

