## How to add or change tokens

1. Edit variables in Figma `Prytula-Responsive` (Mode 1 only).
2. Export variables → save as `design-tokens/data/figma-variables.tsv`.
3. Run `npm run build:tokens` from repo root — regenerates `tokens.css` + `tokens.ts` in both `design-tokens/dist/` and `web/src/styles/`.
4. Verify dev: `cd web && npm run dev` — visual check that nothing broke.
5. Commit `figma-variables.tsv` and any component changes. Do **not** commit generated `tokens.css` (gitignored).
6. Migrating an existing token name? Plan find-replace across `web/src/**/*.module.css` + `web/src/index.css` before bumping.
